data.description: This spacious two-story home sits in a quiet  neighborhood in Summerville.  The foyer is flanked by the formal living room and formal dining room.  Brand new laminate wood flooring throughout the first floor and new carpet on the second along with fresh paint. The eat-in kitchen offers ample cabinet space and a breakfast bar for extra seating. The family room has a fireplace. Sliding glass doors  lead out to a large deck and patio overlooking the fenced back yard.  Fantastic spot for a BBQ. The upstairs master bedroom is very spacious along with the master bath that offers a garden bathtub with separate shower, dual vanities and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a full size bathroom. Large bonus room over garage is a great option for a game room, man cave, or 4th bedroom.
